source /home/cmelton/apps/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/ve/bin/activate
module load java/latest
python /home/cmelton/apps/DynamicDiskCloudSoftware/Worker/Startup.py --S '/usr/java/latest/bin/java -Xmx4g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest -jar /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T BaseRecalibrator -dcov 2 -R /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam -knownSites /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/dbsnp_138.b37.vcf -knownSites /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/hapmap_3.3.b37.vcf -o /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.recalData.grp -nct 4 -L /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/interval.interval_list
/usr/java/latest/bin/java -Xmx8g -Djava.io.tmpdir=/srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest -jar /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/GenomeAnalysisTK.jar -T PrintReads -R /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/g1k_v37_decoy_ref/human_g1k_v37_decoy.fasta -I /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.bam -BQSR /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.recalData.grp -o /srv/gsfs0/scratch/cmelton/DDTest/normal.sorted.dedup.realigned.recal.bam -nct 4 -rf BadCigar' --H $1
